I"›<p>The <code>moon</code> integration tracks the phases of the moon.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To enable the moon sensor, add the following lines to your <code>configuration.yaml</code>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
sensor:
  - platform: moon
</code></pre>
<p>This sensor will return one of the following values:
<code>new_moon</code>, <code>waxing_crescent</code>, <code>first_quarter</code>, <code>waxing_gibbous</code>, <code>full_moon</code>, <code>waning_gibbous</code>, <code>last_quarter</code> or <code>waning_crescent</code> .</p>
